data.description: Great family starter home or vacation get away. Large living area with plenty of wood accents and nice natural light. Large picture window overlooking the completely fenced and landscaped private yard. Nice kitchen with comfortable breakfast nook area. Three bedroom two bath with including a nice size laundry area. Plenty of patio area for summer BBQ's. Landscaped perimeter boasts very nice curb appeal.  Large shed for the wood and garden tools. Covered breezeway to the house from the shed for no slipping.! Nice size garage and plenty of off street parking.  Bring the toys and the family..!
